{"tid":1927924,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"細哨保釋金提高至160萬美元，法官拒絕","createTime":"2020-03-16T05:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T10:06:24.000Z","uid":173952,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b0db24ba803d65519482200f5abc4c4e20977345","tid":1927924,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:39:01.000Z","msg":"獄中的羅納爾迪尼奧和他的兄弟將保釋金的金額提高至160萬美元，但依然被法官古斯塔沃拒絕了。<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div><br />\n<br />\n 上週二，小羅的律師提出80萬保釋金，並以價值80萬美金的豪宅作為擔保，要求保外軟禁。 但被法官古斯塔沃拒絕，因為法官認為該財產和羅納爾迪尼奧並無關係。<br />\n<br />\n 之後，律師將保釋金提高一倍，達到了160萬美元，依舊沒有成功。 小羅使用假護照入境的案件已經涉及了16個人，有10人被捕。"},{"pid":"1bc1457ab1279dadeb6d9e5a75bdecbfb924a518","tid":1927924,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"600萬就豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8a72074e68da358ae026fa923673b40a7c2255","tid":1927924,"uid":351758,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"929e850af7773ee9abd3648aacb7a253e254ef32","tid":1927924,"uid":267880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8d8a72074e68da358ae026fa923673b40a7c2255","tid":1927924,"uid":351758,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"就快有電視台比錢轉播"},{"pid":"d5d30bfe969772f8397e13e9aaddf7b3d490b12c","tid":1927924,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"坐多陣衛冕監獄盃好過啦"},{"pid":"292cee8c81e6c8833a9de7b2bfa8b1343be7a3e5","tid":1927924,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"屌你，踢多幾場波先好出番去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dce6bd3346764943e3eadd2e16d34bfeb16a1eb","tid":1927924,"uid":57674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T06:21:04.000Z","msg":